Rodong Sinmun on Imperialists' Strong-Arm Policy
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 11 (KCNA) -- The imperialists have historically pursued the strong-arm policy for the aggression and plunder of other countries and this policy is bound to prove bankrupt. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Rodong Sinmun Sunday stresses this in a signed article. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 When the division of the territory started by the major capitalist countries in the 60s and 70s of the 19th century was brought to conclusion in the early 20th century, capitalism was converted into imperialism and the United States emerged as the head of imperialism with the Second World War as an occasion, the article notes, and goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. then worked hard to inveigle other imperialist countries into the implementation of its policy for aggression under the deceptive slogan of "defending the free world". It also tried to realize its ambition to dominate the world by subordinating those countries to it through "aid" and organizing military block for aggression. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In the period of the Cold War the U.S. made all its efforts to oppose the socialist countries while raising a hue and cry over the "threat of socialism".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Korean War and Vietnamese War provoked by the U.S. imperialists were typical examples. But the U.S. could not but sustain bitter defeats by the united strength of the revolutionary forces against imperialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The reactionary imperialist forces have intensified the offensive against the independent forces against imperialism after the collapse of the Soviet Union and socialist countries in eastern Europe and in particular, the U.S. which emerged as the "only superpower" in the world has become all the more undisguised in its high-handed and arbitrary practices in the world arena, violating the sovereignty of independent states. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Their offensive was targeted against the DPRK which has invariably held aloft the banner of socialism, banner of independence. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The DPRK people have defended socialism and strikingly demonstrated the dignity and might of the country as they have fought with the formidable imperialist enemy with dignity under the uplifted banner of Songun. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. launched the military aggression against Afghanistan and Iraq under the pretext of the "anti-terror war" aimed at the aggression and plunder of other countries and put those countries under its occupation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 There thus emerged new imperialist method for aggression and gangster-like plunder in the new century. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Today the U.S. seeks the expansion and protraction of the "anti-terror war" to invade by force and dominate the independent countries against imperialism and countries located in the places of strategic importance. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The imperialists' intensified strong-arm policy will bring them worse situation and destruction in the end.

Struggle against Import of American Beef Unabated in S. Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 11 (KCNA) -- Struggle against the import of American beef is going on day after day in south Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A candlelight rally was held at the Chonggye Plaza in Kwanghwamun of Seoul on May 7 under the sponsorship of the People's Measure Council for Opposing the Full Opening of South Korean Market to American Beef in the wake of similar rally on May 6. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The participants accused the present "government" of its crimes against the people not only in the beef problem but education, public health and several other fields, asserting the need for the people to impeach Lee Myung Bak in order to survive. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 At the end of the rally they took part in a signature campaign. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 On May 7 the organization called a press conference in front of the "National Assembly" to demand the probe of the truth behind the negotiations on the import of beef. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Prior to this, representatives of peasant organizations including the Federation of Peasants Associations also called a press conference.

Import of American Beef Opposed in S. Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 10 (KCNA) -- The People's Measure Council for Opposing the Full Opening of South Korean Market to American Beef was inaugurated with due ceremony in Seoul of south Korea on May 6. It comprises over 1 500 political parties and civic and social organizations. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The participants in the ceremony accused the authorities of branding the struggle against the import of the beef as "illegal" and conservative media of distorting truth to defend the "government." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They declared that they would intensify the struggle such as candlelight rally and signature campaign demanding total nullification of the negotiations on the beef and the renegotiation on it and the enactment of a special law at the "National Assembly".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 They urged Lee Myung Bak to make clear background of the negotiations and truth behind them, dismiss those related to them from their posts and make an opening apology to the people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 A rally took place in Seoul on the same day to oppose the import of American beef with the attendance of at least 10 000 citizens from different social standings under the sponsorship of the Headquarters of the All-People Movement for the Impeachment of Lee Myung Bak and a candlelight rally by the members of civic and social organizations including the People's Monitoring Group against American Beef in Danger of Mad Cow Disease and citizens, more than 2 000 in all.

Lee Myung Bak Group's Confrontation Moves Protested in S. Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 10 (KCNA) -- The South Headquarters of the National Alliance of Youth and Students for the Country's Reunification made public a resolution at the extraordinary session of its Central Committee on April 30. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The resolution referred to the fact that the Lee Myung Bak group's moves for confrontation with the fellow countrymen in collusion with the U.S. are throwing a stumbling block in the way of realizing the idea of "By our nation itself." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting that traitor Lee Myung Bak has gone the lengths of revealing his attempt to mount a preemptive attack on the fellow countrymen, the resolution dismissed him as the worst traitor, a stooge serving outsiders and dictatorial fanatic. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It called on youth and students to take the lead in the struggle for frustrating the confrontation moves of the traitorous group as it escalates confrontation with the fellow countrymen and war crisis, adding: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 We will conduct a broad movement to correctly understand the north including its Songun politics so as to arm ourselves with the Korean nation-first spirit and eradicate all the remnants of confrontation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 We will wage dynamic political information service and mass struggle, firmly standing against the authorities' policy for exterminating democracy such as the retrogressive revision of the "law on rally and demonstration" and suppression of pro-reunification patriots.

U.S. State Deputy Secretary's Junket to S. Korea under Fire
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 10 (KCNA) -- The People for Achieving Peace and Reunification of south Korea staged a protest against the visit to south Korea by the U.S. deputy secretary of State in front of the building of the "Ministry of Foreign Affairs and Trade" on May 8. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The organization read out a statement titled "We denounce the U.S. State deputy secretary's south Korean visit for intensified alliance for aggression".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Referring to the fact that the U.S. deputy secretary of State flew in south Korea on May 7, the statement said that the purpose of his visit is to boost the south Korea-U.S. "alliance" for aggression and push forward the realization of the "strategic flexibility" of the U.S. forces present in south Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 No sooner had he arrived in south Korea than he uttered that no beef exported by the U.S. has ever caused any trouble and it is a doubt without scientific ground and the like, the statement said, adding that his utterances were aimed to help the Lee Myung Bak regime shaken by the strong protest of the people against the opening of south Korean market to American beef. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The U.S. should no longer violate the interests of the Korean nation for its ambition for domination, it noted, urging the U.S. to conclude a peace agreement on the Korean Peninsula, withdraw its troops from south Korea and break the "alliance" for aggression. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The moment the U.S. State deputy secretary appeared in front of the building of the ministry, the members of the organization waged a demo shouting slogans such as "We oppose south Korea-U.S. alliance for aggression!"

April Holidays of DPRK Commemorated Worldwide
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 11 (KCNA) -- The world progressives significantly commemorated the 96th birth anniversary of President Kim Il Sung, the 15th anniversary of General Secretary Kim Jong Il's election as chairman of the DPRK National Defence Commission and the 76th birthday of the heroic Korean People's Army in April. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 On those occasions, Kim Jong Il was presented with gifts by organizations and figures of Russia, Ecuador and Myanmar. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
High-ranking figures of different units and political parties, government ministries, the military, institutions and organizations of different countries sent floral baskets to the DPRK missions in their countries or visited them. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Among them were the King and the Great King of Cambodia, the chairwoman of the Central Directive Council of the Indonesian Democratic Party of Struggle, the deputy speaker of the Russian State Duma, the vice-prime minister and minister of Defence of the Lao government, the general secretary of the Party for Unity and Progress of Guinea, the chief of the General Staff of the Armed Forces of Syria and officials of the Ministry of Defence of Vietnam, the Malaysian People's Movement and the el Gaddafi Development Organization of Libya. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Central Committee of the Communist Party of Soviet Union conferred the medal commemorating the 90th anniversary of the great October socialist revolution on the President and Kim Jong Suk, anti-Japanese war hero, and a district council of a province of Cuzco region of Peru and the Atuntaqui City government of Imbabura Province of Ecuador and the Puebla State of Mexico awarded the titles of honorary district head and honorary citizen to the three generals of Mt. Paektu on the occasion of the Day of the Sun. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Organization of Solidarity of the Peoples of Asia, Africa and Latin-America placed a floral basket before a portrait of smiling President with due ceremony and a meeting was held by the Russian Union of Writers to adopt a congratulatory message to Kim Jong Il. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In December last year, the Austrian preparatory committee was formed to commemorate the Day of the Sun in the year 2008 and the Pakistan-Korea Friendship Association and the Paektusan Czech-Korean Friendship Association adopted an appeal and a decision calling for commemorating the birthday of the peerlessly great man as the grand political festival common to mankind and preparatory committees to commemorate the Day of the Sun made up of figures of governments, political parties and organizations were inaugurated in at least 50 countries in response to the call. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Political parties and organizations and public figures of different social standings of various countries released statements on those occasions. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Among them were the chairman of the Central Executive Committee of the Bangladesh National Socialist Party, the chairman of the Misr Arab Socialist Party of Egypt, the president of the Group of Dialectical Materialists of Italy, the Arab Committee for Solidarity with Korean People and Supporting the Reunification of Korea in Jordan. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 There were at least 300 remembrance meetings, rallies, friendly meetings, seminars, lectures, round-table talks, photo exhibitions, film shows and art performances attended by high-ranking officials in over 80 countries and regions and letters and congratulatory messages to Kim Jong Il were adopted at the functions.

Kim Il Sung's Work Off Press in Dominica
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 11 (KCNA) -- President Kim Il Sung's famous work "10-Point Programme of the Great Unity of the Whole Nation for the Reunification of the Country" was brought out in booklet by a publishing house of Dominica on April 28. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The work was published on April 6, Juche 82 (1993).

Joint Seminar on Juche Idea Held in Mexico
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 10 (KCNA) -- A joint seminar on the theme of "The Juche idea is the great idea in the present times guiding the popular masses' struggle for independence" was held in Mexico on May 3. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It was attended by members of the Mexican Committee for the Study of Kimilsungism and the Mexican Institute for the Study of the Juche Idea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Present there on invitation were the secretary general of the International Institute of the Juche Idea and his party on a visit to Mexico and an official of the DPRK embassy in Mexico City. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Speeches were made there. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The speakers profoundly explained that the Juche idea is the great guiding idea, the new philosophical idea in the era of independence as it indicates the way for carving out the destiny of the popular masses and that it is an original idea as it elucidates that man is a social being with independence, creativity and consciousness. They also noted that only when the Juche idea is held fast to as an important guideline, is it possible to put an end to the imperialists' domination and subordination and realize the popular masses' cause of independence. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Noting with high appreciation that this idea has been successfully embodied in the DPRK, they expressed their determination to activate the study and dissemination of the idea and thus contribute to the cause of global independence.

Entidad surcoreana rechaza visita de subsecretario de Estado de EE.UU.
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, 10 de mayo (ATCC) -- Los "Hombres Partidarios de la Paz y la Reunificacion" del Sur de Corea desarrollaron el dia 8 una protesta frente a la sede del "Ministerio de Relaciones Exteriores y Comercio" en contra de la visita del subsecretario de Estado norteamericano al Sur de Corea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  En la ocasion se dio lectura a la declaracion intitulada "Rechazamos la visita del subsecretario de Estado estadounidense con el proposito de fortalecer la alianza para la agresion". &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  El documento se refiere a la llegada al Sur de Corea de ese funcionario estadounidense y destaca que el vino con la intencion de consolidar la "alianza" Sur de Corea-Estados Unidos para la agresion y acelerar todos los preparativos para conseguir la "flexibilidad estrategica" de sus tropas ocupantes del Sur de Corea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  En cuanto arribo al Sur de Corea para ayudar al "gobierno" de Lee Myung Bak tambaleandose por la fuerte resistencia del pueblo a la apertura total del mercado a la carne de res de EE.UU., el visitante dijo que "nunca sucedio problemas en la carne de res de EE.UU. exportada" y que las "sospechas de este producto pecuario carecen de razones cientificas", revela. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Exige que EE.UU. debe dejar de pisotear a la nacion coreana por sus ambiciones dominacionistas, concertar un pacto de paz de la Peninsula Coreana, retirar a sus tropas y romper la "alianza" de agresion. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Cuando el visitante estadounidense hizo su apariencia ante el "Ministerio de Relaciones Exteriores y Comercio", los miembros de la entidad mencionada protestaron gritando las consignas como "!Rechazamos la agresiva alianza Sur de Corea-EE.UU!".

Simposio conjunto sobre idea Juche en Mexico
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, 10 de mayo (ATCC) -- Tuvo lugar el dia 3 en Mexico el simposio conjunto con el topico de "La idea Juche es la grandiosa guia directriz de la epoca actual que orienta la lucha por verificar la independencia de las masas populares".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  En la ocasion estuvieron presentes los miembros del Comite Mexicano de Estudio del Kimilsunismo y del Instituto de la Idea Juche de Mexico. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Fueron invitados el secretario general del Instituto Internacional de la Idea Juche y su comitiva, de visita en Mexico, y un funcionario de la embajada coreana en ese pais. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Los oradores senalaron que la idea Juche es la gran idea directriz y nuevo pensamiento filosofico de la epoca de independencia que ilumina el camino de la forja del destino de las masas populares. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
�@ Agregaron que esa original idea definio al hombre como ente social con la independencia, la creatividad y la conciencia. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
�@ Argumentaron que cuando marcha adelante tomandola por guia directriz,  es posible acabar con el dominio y subyugacion de los imperialistas y cumplir la causa de independencia de las masas populares. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Elogiaron la realidad de Corea donde se materializa brillantemente la idea Juche y expresaron sus decisiones de dinamizar las actividades de estudio y propaganda de la idea Juche y asi contribuir a la realizacion de la causa de independencia del mundo.
